    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This enthusiast-spec example features a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been completed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing kit. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings, maintaining the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and steering feedback. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the powertrain is in peak operational form, delivering linear power all the way to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
