    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that balances reliability with a premium driving experience. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful use. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is soft and intact, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every electronic feature, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, operates perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a consistent service history. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a cooling system flush. This car drives straight and true, offering a comfortable and quiet ride that reflects its careful ownership. It is an honest, dependable vehicle ready for the road.",
